noria:OP_NetworkFailover noria:operationPlanPreCondition noria:APC_TrafficLow ;
    noria:operationPlanPostCondition noria:APOC_ServiceRestored .

noria:OP_DBBackup noria:operationPlanPostCondition noria:APOC_NewConfigActive .

# Link Event Records to proposed repair actions (Operation Plans)
