noria:Event_CPUHigh_WebServer01 noria:alarmProposedRepairAction noria:OP_ServerReboot .

# Link Trouble Tickets to related parties (inverse of noria:troubleTicketRelatedParty)
org:ApplicationSupportTeam noria:troubleTicketRelatedParty noria:TT_WebPortalOutage_001, noria:TT_DBPerformance_003 .
org:NetworkOperationsTeam noria:troubleTicketRelatedParty noria:TT_WebPortalOutage_001, noria:TT_CoreRouterLinkFailure_002, noria:TT_DNSOutage_004 .
org:DatabaseTeam noria:troubleTicketRelatedParty noria:TT_DBPerformance_003 .

