foaf:BobJohnson noria:changeRequestInitiatorParty noria:CR_WebServerOSUpgrade_001 .
org:ApplicationSupportTeam noria:changeRequestPilotParty noria:CR_WebServerOSUpgrade_001 .
org:InfrastructureTeam noria:changeRequestActorParty noria:CR_WebServerOSUpgrade_001 .

foaf:AliceSmith noria:changeRequestInitiatorParty noria:CR_FirewallRuleUpdate_002, noria:CR_BranchNetworkExtension_003 .
